{"tid":882480,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"每次開機風扇都勁嘈 關機再開就靜返","createTime":"2018-10-30T07:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T11:40:57.000Z","uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6658f2fb6624c0584c55b202968f85c088dd5f01","tid":882480,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 部機砌左半年左右<br />\nspec如下<br />\nCPU<br />\n- Intel&reg;️ Core&trade;️ CoffeeLake i7-8700 3.2GHz 12M Cache 6 Core 12 Thread LGA1151\t$2320\t<br />\n主機板<br />\n- ASUS ROG STRIX Z370-H GAMING\t$1680\t<br />\n顯示卡<br />\n- ASUS ROG Strix GeForce&reg;️ GTX 1070 Ti Advanced edition 8GB GDDR5\t$4800 SALES <br />\n$5400\t<br />\nRAM<br />\n- G.SKILL Trident Z RGB Series DDR4 16GB (2 x 8GB) DDR4 3000MHz C15\t$1890\t<br />\n火牛<br />\n- Corsair TX-M Series&trade;️ TX650M 80 Plus&reg;️ Gold 650W Certified PSU\t$769\t<br />\nHDD<br />\n- Toshiba DT01ACA100 1TB 7200rpm 32MB 3.5 Inch HDD\t$320\t<br />\nSSD<br />\n- Samsung PM961 256GB NVMe M.2 SSD\t$765 SALES <br />\n$899\t<br />\n機箱<br />\n- Sharkoon BW9000-G(Black) 黑色 Glass ver.\t$599\t<br />\n散熱<br />\n- GELID PHANTOM BLACK Cpu cooler 幻影黑\t$399<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭半年都無事好靜 就算打高效game開到70度都好靜<br />\n但上兩星期開始一開機就風扇勁嘈 有睇過係機尾同機前兩個都好似係咁 開左塊側板都聽唔出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係bios到較返靜音dc模式只係細聲左少少<br />\n<br />\n始終都係熄左機再開先靜返 jj插沙求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d46cd50c6f142dd3ebd00480fb1b11f0e013360","tid":882480,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e92a73609328ef5593f18250c6f